The names "MakeitSEO", "MakeitSEO Standard", "Agent Runtime Compatibility", and "ARC" (in the context of agent runtime compatibility) are unregistered trademarks of Cloud WiFi Limited. The CC-BY 4.0 licence does not grant trademark rights.

You may refer to the specifications by name when describing your implementation, comparing products, or citing the work. You may not use the names in a way that suggests endorsement by Cloud WiFi Limited, or implies that your product is the official specification, the canonical reference implementation, or otherwise authoritative.

If you describe your product as conformant, the conformance bar is defined inside each specification document. Passing that bar entitles you to a listing in the implementations directory of the relevant specification, which is the official record of conformant implementations.

